title: Press release: Change of British High Commissioner to Canada
text:
Change of British High Commissioner to Canada From: Canada 
Mrs Susan le Jeune d’Allegeershecque CMG has been appointed British High Commissioner to Canada 
Mrs Susan le Jeune d’Allegeershecque CMG has been appointed British High Commissioner to Canada in succession to Mr Howard Drake OBE, who will be retiring from the Diplomatic Service. Mrs le Jeune d’Allegeershecque will take up her appointment in August 2017. Curriculum Vitae Susan Jane le Jeune d’Allegeershecque CMG Married to Stephane Herve Marie le Jeune d’Allegeershecque Children
